premise_source_doc_sentence: Novak Djokovic  (  Новак Ђоковић , Novak Đoković , -LSB- nôʋaːk d͡ʑôːkoʋit͡ɕ -RSB- ; born 22 May 1987  )  , often referred to by the hypocorism Nole , is a Serbian professional tennis player who is currently ranked world No. 2 in men 's singles tennis by the Association of Tennis Professionals  (  ATP  )  .

Josep Pla i Agustí  (  c. 1728 - 1762  )  was a Catalan composer , youngest of three composer-brothers : his older brother Joan Baptista Pla  (  1720-1773  )  , was an oboist in Lisbon , and Manuel Pla  (  c.1725-1766  )  , harpsichordist at the court of Madrid .
